    {
      "id": "1934750c-f3ba-8000-81ee-f61c94419012",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Ther are recommender systems that suggest pedagogical activities to professors. However, the acceptance of these suggestions is not always popular. The recommender proposed in this paper is ontology-based.",
